<h1><img alt="Student Representative Council" src="Images/student-support/SRC/Ambassadors_header.png" /></h1>
<div id="content">
<p>(See the<a href="x40734.xml"> Run for Office page</a> for more information about elections and how to run.)</p>
<p><em>Time Commitment: 10 hours/week &ndash; for 2 semesters</em></p>
<p>The student body officers are elected by a plurality vote open to the entire BYU-Idaho student body every two semesters.</p>
<h2 style="padding-left: 30px;">President</h2>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;">Special Requirements:</p>
<ul style="padding-left: 30px;">
<li>Served as a volunteer for the Student Representative Council.</li>
<li>Served as a <em>director </em>or higher in a different BYU-Idaho student led organization.</li>
<li>See the <a href="x36371.xml">Elections Policy</a> for additional requirements.</li>
</ul>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;">The Student Body President leads the Student Representative Council, the Student Leadership Council, directly oversees the work of the Student Voice,&nbsp;and represents the students of BYU-Idaho as a member of the President&rsquo;s Council and University Council.</p>
<h2 style="padding-left: 30px;">Vice President</h2>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;">Special Requirements:</p>
<ul>
<li>Served as a volunteer for the Student Representative Council.</li>
<li>Served in a different BYU-Idaho student led organization at the "program manager" level or higher.</li>
<li>See the <a href="x36371.xml">Elections Policy</a> for additional requirements.</li>
</ul>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;">The Student Body Vice President assists the president in leading the Student Representative Council, supervises the&nbsp;involvement in administrative councils and the research activity of the Student Representatives, and represents the students of BYU-Idaho as amember of the Student Well-Being Council.</p>
</div>
